INSERT INTO `drinks` (`id`, `NAME`, `user_id`, `description`, `image_url`) VALUES (NULL, 'Red Lable', '2', 'In 1909, \'Special Old Highland Whisky\' was renamed Johnnie Walker Red Label and a legend was born. Imbued with pioneering spirit from the outset, Johnnie Walker Red Label travelled \"wherever ship could sail\". With its bold flavour and versatile character, it mixed well socially and made friends all around the globe.', 'https://cavashopcyprus.com/images/stories/virtuemart/product/johnnie_walker_red_label.jpg'), (NULL, 'Baileys', '3', 'The Baileys Story. Every year, roughly 200 million liters of milk go into the fresh cream we use for Baileys Original Irish Cream and its variants. We only partner with local Irish farmers since 1974. It\'s just one reason why Baileys ingredients are so delicious.', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/58/Glass_of_Baileys.jpg/330px-Glass_of_Baileys.jpg'), (NULL, 'Chivas Regal', '4', 'Chivas Regal 12 Year Old Blended Scotch Whisky - Chivas Regal US Tasting Notes Cask Finish A variety of casks are used for maturation of the 12-year-old Scotch whiskies that make up this blend, leading to a greater depth and character. Nose An aromatic infusion of wild herbs, heather, honey and orchard fruits. Palate', 'https://external-content.duckduckgo.com/iu/?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftse1.mm.bing.net%2Fth%3Fid%3DOIP.krvOQrDhhxfx8nrk_uUG0QHaHa%26pid%3DApi%26h%3D160&f=1&ipt=c61e3ed126cdaa3c8bc0a387a5415f8486ddbcb8cf492d9d8162f9ecdcab47e6&ipo=images'), (NULL, 'Chanceler Whiskey', '5', 'At Whiskey Bar Store we are proud to offer the highest level of service to our customers, online. We sell over 300 single malt , blended whiskies including Scotch whisky, American Bourbon whiskey, Irish whiskey , vodka and more . Categories Whiskey Blended Scotch Bourbons & Tennessee Malts Lebanese Whiskey Irish Whiskey Wine Red Wine Rose Wine', 'https://external-content.duckduckgo.com/iu/?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftse1.mm.bing.net%2Fth%3Fid%3DOIP.NKUAIdLt-YJxlijPK7kNdgHaK2%26pid%3DApi%26h%3D160&f=1&ipt=9f3728ec919903a502d10216a9cce3cbd9c75c12ed61ca22aba58bb1aa63c893&ipo=images'), (NULL, ' Balblair', '1', 'At Balblair, we\'ve always taken our time to make our single malt. Together with this commitment, we celebrate the role our Highland home plays in shaping the character of our whisky. About Our Distillery Quality comes before all else We purposefully don\'t seek to make a lot of our extraordinary whisky.', 